title: Elizabeth Munnerlyn
text: Elizabeth Munnerlyn is <a href="Democratic%20Party%20%28United%20States%29">Democratic</a> politician from <a href="South%20Carolina">South Carolina</a>. She was a member of the <a href="South%20Carolina%20House%20of%20Representatives">South Carolina House of Representatives</a> from 2011 to 2014. Munnerlyn was previously an assistant solicitor for the <a href="United%20States%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20for%20the%20Fourth%20Circuit">fourth circuit</a>.
